About this item

    This fits your .
  • Make sure this fits by entering your model number.
  • USB Hub 3.0: UGREEN 4-Port USB 3.0 Hub simply helps you to connect up to 4 USB devices to your PC or Laptop, such as external hard drives, USB flash drives, mouse, keyboard, USB headphone, speakers, memory cards, keyboard, mouse and much more USB devices etc. It keeps you away from the trouble of plugging& unplugging repeatly.
  • Slim, Light & Portable: This USB hub Weighs only 2.08 ounces (included package) and measures 10.4*3*1 cm, which is compact, portable and convinient, ideal for your traveling with ultrabook.
  • 5Gbps Data Transfer Speed: USB 3.0 data hub supports super faster data transfer up to 5Gbps - 10X faster than USB 2.0 (480 Mbps), which allows you to transfer HD movies or large files in just seconds. It is backward compatible with USB 2.0, 1.1 and 1.0. Through the LED indicator, you can easily monitor the connection status.
  • External Micro USB Power Port Supply: This USB data hub could be powered by your 5V USB power adapter, easily connect it with micro usb charger and cord, don't need to worry about insufficient power supply of 2.5" and 3.5" HDD. (Note: Power adapter and micro USB cable are NOT included)
  • Great Compatibility: 4-port USB data hub is compatible with Windows10/(32/64 bit) 8.1 / 8 / 7 / Vista / XP, Mac OS X 10.6 to 10.9, Linux 2.6.14 or above, plug and play.

Product Description

Read more
Read more

USB 3.0 Ports Expansion

  • - Turn one of your computer's USB ports into four.
  • - 4 USB devices can be connected at the same time.
  • - White LED to indicate the working status of this USB 3.0 hub.

Stable and Safe

  • - Multi shielding to ensure stable transmission, no interference, and no delay.
  • - Over-voltage, over-current protection, ensure the safety of your data and devices.

Kindly Note

  • - This USB 3.0 hub is designed for data sync only, not for charging.
  • - The micro USB cable to power this hub or extension cable to extend this hub should be shorter than 1M.
  • - 2.4GHz wireless devices, MIDI devices and some USB 3.0 devices may not be supported.
  • - To ensure high performance for HDD, SSD and other power-hungry devices, extra main power is needed. (Power adapter and power cable sold separately).

Specification

  • Material: ABS
  • Connector: USB 3.0
  • Interface: USB 3.0 * 4
  • Cable Length: 16CM
  • Dimensions (L*W*H): 10.4*3*1 cm

      Amazonuser
      5.0 out of 5 stars Quality USB Hub.
      Reviewed in the United States on June 26, 2020
      Verified Purchase
      Works great if you need more USB ports like I did on a Surface Pro 4 which gives you just one. This will split one into four ports and offers speeds up to 5gb/s. (Speeds vary on what type of USB port you use and the devices you are using.)

      Example. Using this plugged into USB 2.0 ports will impact speeds and power available to the usb port you are using will impact your performance of devices. Same in reverse. If you use an older device that does not support those high speeds, you will never see the top speeds.

      When you use this, you must keep in mind the number of devices you can use depends on your USB power port. (Not all created equal.) Some have less power than others.

      USB 1 and 2 will go to about 500mAh, USB 3.0 can go to 900 mAh and USB 3.1 can go upwards of 3000 mAh or 3 amps.

      Saying that, I am able to run a Micro 32gb Samsung USB drive, connect a phone usb adapter and use it to connect a usb to HDMI graphics adapter.

      If you are using numerous devices and experience an issue, just plug in a Micro USB cord to a computer or wall adapter to give you the extra power you need.

      As always, I will update this review should this fail with ongoing use or develop issues.

      1.0 out of 5 stars Crashed a 2TB hard drive
      Reviewed in the United States on March 19, 2020
      Verified Purchase
      The first one of these we returned when we realized one of the four ports was bad. I'm an engineer; I understand sometimes there are defects. No big deal. We returned it. Amazon sent us another. It was super easy. Replacement arrives. We're good.
      Until 6 months later, our 2TB hard drive crashes. At first I thought it was tough luck and didn't realize this hub caused the crash. Then I hooked a camera up to the same port the crashed hard drive was plugged in and it starts cutting out. So this replacement ends up with the exact same problem; one of the ports starts cutting power on and off. By the way, that destroys any storage device without its own power (hard drive, flash drive, card reader, etc.). We lost several hundreds of pictures, business records, and data between backups. Do not buy this if you want to hook anything off value to it!

      Reviewed in Mexico on May 20, 2020
      Verified Purchase
      El concentrador USB 3.0 es bastante práctico, te permite obtener 4 puertos USB3.0 a partir de uno solo. El concentrador está hecho en plástico resistente. Ideal para laptops.

      IMPORTANTE: Si conectas 2 o más equipos al concentrador/hub, dispositivos que consuman muchacorriente (ej: discos duros mecánicos, tu celular cargando), ES sugerido que conectes una fuente de poder de unos 5V@2A en el puerto micro-usb que tiene el concentrador UGREEN USB 3.0, de otra forma, puedes tener intermitencia --- esto es, que tus discos se apaguen/desconecten y reconecten repetidamente, al no recibir suficiente corriente para permanecer encendidos y conectados.

      He adquirido otros hubs de 7 puertos USB 3.0 y más y NO los recomendaría, son algo inestables en los dispositivos se desconectan aleatoriamente. En cambio, el UGREEN de 4 puertos USB 3.0 es adecuado para tener tus equipos encendidos las 24hrs sin problema alguno.
